c: 33
v: 73
t: "Kagiya ziksaan o Allah so manga monapik a manga mama, go so manga monapik a manga babay, go so manga pananakoto a manga mama, go so manga pananakoto a manga babay, go phakatawbatn o Allah so miyamaratiyaya a manga mama, go so miyamaratiyaya a manga babay: Na tatap a so Allah na Manapi, a Makalimoon"